Line Card IPC Development Notes

Use the following command to create test port in SUP:
    test ipc port create <port no> zone <zone_id>
Use zone_id 0


The SM Control is a special port.
All control message should go to this port.
Control messages that needs to be forwarded to IPC Master will first be
placed on the out_que.

Other data packets to SUP will not be put on the out_que.



For message destinated to the IPC control port, no actual open is done.
The port index will always be zero.



